n\"\n  if tmux has-session -t primary 2>/dev/null\n    if test -n \"$TMUX\"\n      tmux switch-client -t primary\n    else\n      tmux attach-session -t primary\n    end\n  else\n    tmuxinator start primary\n  end\nend\n```\n\nSame pattern for `_tmo_function` (`mobile`), `_tdo_function` (`desktop`), `_two_function` (`work`).\n\n### 4. Update `_tss_function.fish` (sessionizer)\n\nFor default sessions use tmuxinator; for ad-hoc sessions fall back to plain `tmux new-session`:\n\n```fish\nfunction _tss_function --description \"Fuzzy-pick or create a tmux session\"\n  set -l default_sessions primary mobile desktop work\n\n  set -l existing (tmux list-sessions -F '#S' 2>/dev/null)\n  set -l candidates $default_sessions\n  for s in $existing\n    if not contains $s $default_sessions\n      set -a candidates $s\n    end\n  end\n\n  set -l selected (printf '%s\\n' $candidates | fzf --prompt=\"session> \" --height=40%)\n\n  if test -n \"$selected\"\n    if tmux has-session -t \"$selected\" 2>/dev/null\n      if test -n \"$TMUX\"\n        tmux switch-client -t \"$selected\"\n      else\n        tmux attach-session -t \"$selected\"\n      end\n    else if contains $selected $default_sessions\n      tmuxinator start \"$selected\"\n    else\n      tmux new-session -d -s \"$selected\"\n      if test -n \"$TMUX\"\n        tmux switch-client -t \"$selected\"\n      else\n        tmux attach-session -t \"$selected\"\n      end\n    end\n  end\nend\n```\n\n## Files to Modify/Create\n| File | Action |\n|------|--------|\n| `home-manager/programs/tmux/default.nix` | Add `home.packages = [ pkgs.tmuxinator ]` + `xdg.configFile` entries |\n| `home-manager/programs/tmux/tmuxinator/primary.yml` | **create** |\n| `home-manager/programs/tmux/tmuxinator/mobile.yml` | **create** |\n| `home-manager/programs/tmux/tmuxinator/desktop.yml` | **create** |\n| `home-manager/programs/tmux/tmuxinator/work.yml` | **create** |\n| `home-manager/programs/fish/functions/_tpo_function.fish` | Update to use tmu